trans-unit.source: Converts service, contract, and endpoint information into metadata documents.
trans-unit.target: Converte as informações de serviço, o contrato e o ponto de extremidade em documentos de metadados.

trans-unit.source: Use the WsdlExporter class to transform <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription> or <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint> objects into metadata represented by <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSection> objects.
trans-unit.target: Use a classe WsdlExporter para transformar <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription>ou <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint>objetos nos metadados representado por <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSection>objetos.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSection> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription>

trans-unit.source: The WsdlExporter is used in a three-step process.
trans-unit.target: O WsdlExporter é usado em um processo de três etapas.

trans-unit.source: Call the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportContract%2A>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoint%2A>, or <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoints%2A> method, passing the appropriate parameters.
trans-unit.target: Chamar o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportContract%2A>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoint%2A>, ou <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoints%2A>método, passando os parâmetros apropriados.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoints%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoint%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportContract%2A>

trans-unit.source: Determine whether there are any export errors by checking the base <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataExporter.Errors%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Determinar se há erros de exportação, verificando a base de <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataExporter.Errors%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataExporter.Errors%2A>

trans-unit.source: If there are no errors, use the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GetGeneratedMetadata%2A> to get a collection of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSection> objects or get more specific versions of the metadata using the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GeneratedWsdlDocuments%2A> or <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GeneratedXmlSchemas%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Se não houver nenhum erro, use o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GetGeneratedMetadata%2A>para obter uma coleção de <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSection>objetos ou obter versões mais específicas de metadados usando o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GeneratedWsdlDocuments%2A>ou <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GeneratedXmlSchemas%2A>Propriedades.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GeneratedXmlSchemas%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GeneratedWsdlDocuments%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSection> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GetGeneratedMetadata%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can support exporting custom WSDL extensions by implementing the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension> interface and custom policy assertions by implementing the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IPolicyExportExtension> interface.
trans-unit.target: Você pode dar suporte a exportação extensões WSDL personalizadas implementando a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension>interface e declarações de política personalizada com a implementação de <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IPolicyExportExtension>interface.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IPolicyExportExtension> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension>

trans-unit.source: For details, see the documentation for those interfaces.
trans-unit.target: Para obter detalhes, consulte a documentação para essas interfaces.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The `WsdlExporter` can only be used to export metadata from `ContractDescription` instances that contain Common Language Runtime (CLR) type information, such as a `ContractDescription` instance created using the `ContractDescription.GetContract` method or created as part of the `ServiceDescription` for a `ServiceHost` instance.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > O `WsdlExporter` só pode ser usado para exportar metadados de `ContractDescription` instâncias que contêm o Common Language Runtime (CLR) digite informações, como um `ContractDescription` instância criada usando o `ContractDescription.GetContract` método ou criado como parte do `ServiceDescription` para um `ServiceHost` instância.

trans-unit.source: You cannot use the `WsdlExporter` to export metadata from `ContractDescription` instances imported from service metadata or constructed without type information.
trans-unit.target: Não é possível usar o `WsdlExporter` para exportar metadados de `ContractDescription` instâncias importados de metadados de serviço ou construída sem informações de tipo.
